URL p√∫blica lead na Meetime: {{ $item("0").$node["Webhook"].json["body"]["prospection"]["lead"]["publicUrl"] }}

=Anota√ß√µes deixadas por {{ $item("0").$node["Webhook"].json["body"]["prospection"]["salesman"]["name"] }} na Meetime: 

{{ 
(() => {
  const text = $item("0").$node["Webhook"].json["body"]["prospection"]["lead"]["annotations"];
  
  // Primeiro: decodificar caracteres especiais
  let cleaned = text
    .replace(/–/g, '‚Äì')
    .replace(/í/g, '√≠')
    .replace(/ç/g, '√ß')
    .replace(/ã/g, '√£')
    .replace(/õ/g, '√µ')
    .replace(/á/g, '√°')
    .replace(/é/g, '√©')
    .replace(/ó/g, '√≥')
    .replace(/ú/g, '√∫')
    .replace(/ê/g, '√™')
    .replace(/ô/g, '√¥')
    .replace(/&/g, '&')
    .replace(/ /g, ' ')
    .replace(/É/g, '√â'); // Corrige o É que apareceu

  // Processar tags HTML e converter para \n literais
  cleaned = cleaned
    .replace(/<h[1-6][^>]*>/gi, '\\n') // Headers viram \n
    .replace(/<\/h[1-6]>/gi, '\\n')
    .replace(/<p[^>]*>/gi, '\\n')
    .replace(/<\/p>/gi, '\\n')
    .replace(/<br\s*\/?>/gi, '\\n')
    .replace(/<ul[^>]*>/gi, '\\n')
    .replace(/<\/ul>/gi, '\\n')
    .replace(/<li[^>]*>/gi, '\\n‚Ä¢ ') // List items com \n e bullet
    .replace(/<\/li>/gi, '\\n')
    .replace(/<hr[^>]*>/gi, '\\n---\\n')
    .replace(/<[^>]*>/g, ' ') // Remove todas outras tags
    .replace(/\s+/g, ' ') // Remove m√∫ltiplos espa√ßos
    .trim();

  // Adicionar quebras l√≥gicas baseadas nos emojis/se√ß√µes
  cleaned = cleaned
    .replace(/(üîé|üß©|üéØ|üí°|ü§î|üìÖ)/g, '\\n$1')
    .replace(/\s*\.\s*/g, '. ')
    .replace(/\s*,\s*/g, ', ')
    .replace(/\s*:\s*/g, ': ');

  return cleaned;
})()
}}
